pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  # 左侧细竖线
  - elementId: content-left-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 6, 720]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  # 顶部细蓝线
  - elementId: content-top-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [0, 0, 1280, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  # 章节名右上角小字
  - elementId: content-section-name
    elementType: text
    bounds: [900, 16, 340, 22]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: 01 研究背景与问题提出

  # 页面标题
  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 24, 840, 36]
    content:
      fontSize: 26
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>研究背景：问题的提出与意义</strong></p>

  - elementId: title-separator
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 68, 1200, 1]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$borderGray"

  # 四格网格布局
  # 卡片1（左上）
  - elementId: card-1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 82, 580, 270]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightGray"

  - elementId: card-1-label
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 82, 90, 28]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: card-1-label-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 82, 90, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: 现实问题

  - elementId: card-1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [56, 122, 548, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>现实驱动背景</strong></p>

  - elementId: card-1-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [56, 158, 548, 170]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      lineHeight: 1.7
      text: |
        <p>随着XX领域的快速发展，传统方法在应对YY挑战时暴露出明显不足，迫切需要提出新的解决方案。</p>

  # 卡片2（右上）
  - elementId: card-2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [660, 82, 580, 270]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightGray"

  - elementId: card-2-label
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [660, 82, 90, 28]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$secondary"

  - elementId: card-2-label-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [660, 82, 90, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: 理论意义

  - elementId: card-2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [676, 122, 548, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>理论创新意义</strong></p>

  - elementId: card-2-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [676, 158, 548, 170]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      lineHeight: 1.7
      text: |
        <p>本研究从理论层面提出了新的模型框架，丰富了XX领域的方法体系，具有重要的学术价值。</p>

  # 卡片3（左下）
  - elementId: card-3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 372, 580, 270]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightGray"

  - elementId: card-3-label
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [40, 372, 90, 28]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: card-3-label-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [40, 372, 90, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: 应用价值

  - elementId: card-3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [56, 412, 548, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>工程应用价值</strong></p>

  - elementId: card-3-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [56, 448, 548, 170]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      lineHeight: 1.7
      text: |
        <p>研究成果可直接应用于AA、BB等实际场景，有望在CC领域产生直接的工程落地效益。</p>

  # 卡片4（右下）
  - elementId: card-4-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [660, 372, 580, 270]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [4000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$lightGray"

  - elementId: card-4-label
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [660, 372, 90, 28]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#455A64"

  - elementId: card-4-label-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [660, 372, 90, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: 研究目标

  - elementId: card-4-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [676, 412, 548, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>本研究核心目标</strong></p>

  - elementId: card-4-content
    elementType: text
    bounds: [676, 448, 548, 170]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: true
      lineHeight: 1.7
      text: |
        <p>设计并验证一套能有效解决YY问题的方法，在保证精度的前提下显著提升效率。</p>

  # 页码
  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1200, 680, 50, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "4"
